[[!meta title="SentenceNav"]]

* Author: Tony Malykh
* Download [stable version][1]

     SentenceNav is an NVDA add-on that allows you to read text by 
sentences, as opposed to by paragraphs or words.
     Please note that "Jump to next  paragraph with text" feature has 
been move to [TextNav](http://github.com/mltony/nvda-text-nav/) add-on 
that needs to be installed separately.
     Keystrokes
     * Alt+Down: Go to next sentence.
     * Alt+Up: Go to previous sentence.
     * NVDA+Alt+S: Speak current sentence.
     * Alt+Windows+Down: Go to next phrase.
     * Alt+Windows+Up: Go to previous phrase.

